{
	unsigned short i;
	unsigned int crc_result=0xffffffff;
	while(length--)
	{
		crc_result ^= *data++;
		for(i=0;i<8;i++)
		{
			if(crc_result & 0x0001)
			{
				crc_result = (crc_result>>1) ^ 0xa0000001;
			}
			else
			{
				crc_result = crc_result>>1;
			}			
		}
	}
	return (crc_result);		
}
